Description: Rim and neck sherd of Milesian Fikellura pottery oinochoe; trace of light moulding at lower break; white slip; interior: wide band at rim; exterior: top and outside of slightly everted rim glazed; below, meander frieze to left between bands.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GF.125)
